    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Space Pirates for Life</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crash-landed. Outnumbered. Outgunned.<br>You are a space pirate stranded on a bizarre alien planet where every step could be your last. <strong>Hack, slash, and platform your way through a relentless retro-style gauntlet built for hardcore players.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not for the casual gamer. Are you up for the challenge?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Tight 2D combat &amp; precision platforming</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶 <strong>Exclusive unlockable track from Tidal Rave</strong> — only in this game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏃 <strong>Speedrunning in mind</strong> — built-in timers, stats, and replayability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>For true challengers</strong> — deaths are part of the journey</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📊 <strong>End-game stats</strong> to track your performance and bragging rights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔊 <strong>Catchy retro-inspired soundtrack</strong> to fuel your runs</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Why Play?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you love <strong>Celeste, Hollow Knight, or Super Meat Boy</strong>, and you crave the rush of mastering brutal levels, <i>Space Pirates for Life</i> is for you.<br>Every death teaches you. Every run makes you faster. Every victory feels earned.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💾 <strong>Add to your Wishlist now</strong> and prove you have what it takes to survive.<i> </i></p>",
